SubjectCFIA-PIPSC - Informatics Group ** Collective Agreement **
PrecisOrder authorizing the renewal of the COLLECTIVE AGREEMENT between the CANADIAN FOOD INSPECTION AGENCY AND THE PROFESSIONAL INSTITUTE OF THE PUBLIC SERVICE OF CANADA covering employees in the Informatics Group Bargaining Unit. This agreement is for a term of three (3) years from June 1, 2011 to May 31, 2014.
